<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>"Magic" does not mean that it has magical properties or that all classes can wear it.  All that it signifies is that the only way to get it is to loot it from a mob or, I think, from a quest involving loot.  Magic items cannot be bought from merchants, tinkered, or made.</font></td></tr></table>
